easyGlove

Hanjo Odendaal

11/04/2022

Overview

Repository to make the GloVe: Global Vectors for Word Representation model implemented by text2vex more accessible.

Installation

devtools::install_github("HanjoStudy/easyGlove")
library(easyGlove)

Example

Libraries

library(tidyverse)
library(easyGlove)

Data

out <- read_lines("https://www.gutenberg.org/files/2701/2701-0.txt")

Run Model

set.seed(1)
word_vectors <- model_glove(out, ngrams = 2,
                   term_count_min = 5,
                   skip_grams_window = 10L,
                   runs = 10,
                   cores = 14)

Closest Word Vectors

word_sim <- word_vectors %>% 
  glove_closest_to(., "whale", top_n = 100)
